reviewText: Packaged well and delivered fast.  Excellent quality and value.
Wonderful sing a long fun with classic modern songs form the 90's.
We got the tape which plays good, our kids are happy.. even it was old one! This is very good for kids watch & learn too! Thank you & have a nice day!
Love all the Mr. Magoo classics.  They are well put together and you don't have to worry about kids seeing something unsavory.

I love this video as it has some of the best songs from the Disney Renissance. Although I wish it had songs from The Great Mouse Detective and Oliver & Company and other songs from the other films. It seems weird to have Hercules songs on this volume since they weren't released in the US at the time, but in other countries the songs had been in a foreign Disney Sing Along Songs volume, "Hercules" (which was never released in the US although Zero to Hero would be in "Honor to Us All" a year later). Here is the list of songs:
1. Circle of Life (The Lion King)
2. Be Our Guest (Beauty and the Beast)
3. One Last Hope (Hercules)
4. Under the Sea (The Little Mermaid)
5. A Whole New World (Aladdin)
6. Topsy Turvy (The Hunchback of Notre Dame)
7. Colors of the Wind (Pocahontas)
8. Prince Ali (Aladdin)
9. Part of Your World (The Little Mermaid)
10. Zero to Hero (Hercules)
This is a MUST HAVE for girl toddlers who LOVE Ariel & all Disney movie songs! Our twins WATCH it EVERYDAY! Sure wish it was available on dvd?
Wish these were available on DVD for ease of travel.  These three older collections are the best of Disney Classics!!! Parents and Grandparents will know these too!
